  "title": "Principal Consultant",
  "description": "<p>- Overall 10+ years of experience with 4-6 years of extensive experience in Temenos Triple’A Plus administration</p><p>- Manage and maintain the Temenos Triple’A Plus environment (production, test, and development).<br /><br />- Perform configuration, patching, upgrades, and deployments within the TAP platform. Monitor system health, performance, and logs; troubleshoot and resolve issues<br /><br />- Solid understanding of TAP system architecture, application setup, and components.</p><p>-Experience with Unix/Linux environments, Oracle databases, and TAP scripting/config tools.<br /><br />-Familiarity with ITIL practices, especially in change/release management. Strong troubleshooting and analytical skills.<br /><br />-Experience with job schedulers (e.g., Contro Autosys), monitoring tools, and version control (e.g., Git)</p>",
